1
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:52,960
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,620 --> 00:00:56,060
[Episode 1]

3
00:00:56,110 --> 00:00:57,520
Long time no see.

4
00:00:58,790 --> 00:01:00,000
How have you all been,

5
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,110
my old friends?

6
00:01:04,590 --> 00:01:06,120
I slept for a very long time.

7
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:08,310
Now that I'm awake again...

8
00:01:10,910 --> 00:01:12,140
I can't remember

9
00:01:11,670 --> 00:01:14,220
[Episode 1: Convenience Store 444]

10
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,560
what year it is, or any of the things

11
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,950
that happened before.

12
00:01:17,510 --> 00:01:18,680
Where am I?

13
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,070
This is a place of the void,

14
00:01:22,510 --> 00:01:24,110
called the Sea of Illusions.

15
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,480
Only in the illusion

16
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:28,430
can we reunite.

17
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:31,310
I am fortunate to see you again.

18
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:32,470
[Ya]

19
00:01:33,509 --> 00:01:34,200
Yes.

20
00:01:35,310 --> 00:01:36,789
They should all be here,

21
00:01:37,710 --> 00:01:39,350
waiting for a reunion.

22
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:44,910
After that farewell,

23
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,039
[Convenience Store 444]

24
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:47,310
I never saw Zhao Li again.

25
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,690
Ya and I got married,

26
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,620
and we have been living a normal life.

27
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:54,509
We opened a café.

28
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:56,410
To commemorate,

29
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,950
I named it

30
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,680
Convenience Store 444.

31
00:01:58,830 --> 00:02:02,050
[Xia Dongqing]

32
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,790
Convenience Store 444

33
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,040
is still attracting some

34
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,710
strange customers.

35
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:11,400
Hello.

36
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:13,120
This is our special

37
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,400
Coffee 444.

38
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:16,360
It's limited every day.

39
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,550
You are lucky.

40
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,130
This is the last cup.

41
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,600
Want to try it?

42
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:21,910
I bought water.

43
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,000
It's on the house.

44
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,560
Today

45
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,260
is the last day of the year.

46
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:28,840
Are you hitting on me?

47
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,890
Uncle, how old are you?

48
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,590
Caffeine inhibits

49
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,090
A-ped activity in my body,

50
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,630
preventing cAMP from breaking down

51
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,870
and prolonging the effect

52
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:37,730
of adrenaline.

53
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:38,840
What do you mean?

54
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,560
I'm afraid

55
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,329
my heart may beat too fast.

56
00:02:44,550 --> 00:02:46,680
My heart is already beating very fast.

57
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,630
You are waiting for someone?

58
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:58,800
A... man?

59
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:02,590
Trust me.

60
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,330
In terms of love,

61
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,560
it's better not to use these.

62
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:08,680
What do you mean?

63
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:09,470
I think

64
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,290
you are troubled by love

65
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:13,600
and want to use magic

66
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,230
to make someone love you.

67
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:17,090
Don't touch it!

68
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,680
This is my magic formation!

69
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,150
You don't understand.

70
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:21,150
On New Year's Eve,

71
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,850
when the clock strikes,

72
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,870
the living and the dead

73
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,000
can meet.

74
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,840
Then are you a living person
or a dead person?

75
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,770
If I'm waiting for a living person,

76
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,960
I am a dead person.

77
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,079
If I'm waiting for a dead person,

78
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,240
I am a living person.

79
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,120
Take a guess—

80
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,030
am I dead

81
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,520
or alive?

82
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:54,240
Sir,

83
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,210
you have a customer.

84
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,030
Honey.

85
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,430
Honey!

86
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,880
Did you miss me today?

87
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,350
Sorry.

88
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,610
I was too busy and forgot about you.

89
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,230
So sweet.

90
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,040
It's the last day of the year.

91
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,970
How's business?

92
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,730
Sir, what are you looking for?

93
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,930
Who are you looking for?

94
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,400
Who are you looking for?

95
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,430
Wait!

96
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:47,130
What exactly are you looking for?

97
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
Have you seen her?

98
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,510
Who is she to you?

99
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,440
My name is Li Lei.

100
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:58,430
Her name is Han Meimei.

101
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,630
She's my girlfriend.

102
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,560
Is she still in the human world?

103
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,870
Are you crazy?

104
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,820
We are sophomores

105
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,700
at Huazhong Medical University.

106
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,720
She must have been here.

107
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,120
Han Meimei! Han Meimei!

108
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,190
Young man, keep your voice down!

109
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,000
-Han Meimei!
-Stop shouting!

110
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,800
This is my shop!

111
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,270
Come out!

112
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,390
Calm down. Stop shouting.

113
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,040
Come out!

114
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,000
Han Meimei!

115
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,190
Han...

116
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:28,970
What...

117
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,500
What...

118
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,760
What's going on?

119
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,159
Why am I floating in the air?

120
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,490
Who the hell are you?

121
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,430
You are not welcome in our shop.

122
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:50,010
If you come to make trouble again,

123
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:50,720
it won't be as simple

124
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,480
as throwing you out.

125
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,340
Did you hear me?

126
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,880
You must be Li Lei's girlfriend, right?

127
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:04,000
Why did he come here?

128
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,520
How did he know I'm here?

129
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,920
I thought you had left.

130
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,180
I went to the restroom.

131
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:09,830
It's almost the new year.

132
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,630
I can't leave.

133
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,360
I will see him very soon.

134
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:18,600
So you are seeing another man

135
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:20,480
behind your boyfriend's back.

136
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,560
Li Lei is my ex-boyfriend.

137
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,920
We have already broken up.

138
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,040
Are you sure you broke up?

139
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,120
Very sure.

140
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,430
This only shows
your intention to break up.

141
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,870
She cheated on him anyway.

142
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:34,040
I didn't!

143
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,920
Han Meimei!

144
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,480
You cheated on me!

145
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,190
Li Lei?

146
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,680
How do you know I'm here?

147
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,810
Are you stalking me?

148
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:41,720
I know!

149
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:43,040
You must be here to see

150
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,120
that GB38!

151
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,190
GB38?

152
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,830
Is it a screen name?

153
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:47,960
Sounds unreliable.

154
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,360
How do you know?

155
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,040
You stole my diary?

156
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,630
October 28th.

157
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,360
I couldn't help but take

158
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,620
another look at GB38.

159
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,360
He is absolutely perfect.

160
00:06:59,360 --> 00:06:59,920
Stop reading!

161
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,680
I couldn't take my eyes

162
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,950
off him!

163
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,980
November 10th.

164
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:03,920
I can't use words to describe

165
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,850
his perfection.

166
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:06,310
I don't think I could ever

167
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,480
know another man

168
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,960
so thoroughly in my life.

169
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,570
-He's calm.
-Shut up!

170
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:11,630
He's good at listening.

171
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,830
He never talks too much!

172
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:15,000
I can't help but think of Li Lei.

173
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,750
He's too noisy,

174
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:17,720
childish,

175
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:18,880
unintelligent,

176
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,450
and emotionally unstable!

177
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,070
I want to break up with him!

178
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:22,950
Li Lei!

179
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,190
I'll kill you!

180
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,190
Li Lei!

181
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,710
Give me back my diary!

182
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,390
-Tomorrow...
-Give me back my diary!

183
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,390
is New Year's Eve!

184
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
I must see you!

185
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,510
Give it back!

186
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:33,670
You know what?

187
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,600
There is a café

188
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:35,360
called

189
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,560
Convenience Store 444.

190
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,920
Give it back to me!

191
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,120
Shameless thief!

192
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,240
We've already broken up!

193
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,510
You have no right to interfere!

194
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,640
You're too willful!

195
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,250
Breaking up just like that?

196
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,220
Do you know him?

197
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,750
How many years have we known each other?

198
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,680
I don't know him,

199
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,950
but I know you!

200
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,890
We're not right for each other!

201
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:53,920
Don't go yet!

202
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,120
-Don't touch my bag!
-Why are we not right for each other?

203
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,780
-Don't touch my bag!
-Tell me!

204
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,630
It's just a skull specimen.

205
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,040
GB38?

206
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:16,370
Don't touch it!

207
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,390
Give it back to me!

208
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:20,920
Li Lei,

209
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,390
please remember,

210
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,750
we've already broken up.

211
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,210
Please stop pestering me.

212
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:25,770
If you keep this up,

213
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:26,800
I'll only hate you more,

214
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,400
and we can't even be friends!

215
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:46,630
Why did she treat me like that?

216
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:51,440
What right does she have
to treat me like that?

217
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,790
Young man,

218
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:02,510
that girl isn't quite right.

219
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:03,630
You can just find someone else.

220
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:04,910
How could you say that?

221
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:05,910
Do you know her?

222
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:08,000
How could you casually judge someone?

223
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,930
I don't know her.

224
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:09,750
I don't.

225
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,150
I love GB38.

226
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,150
I want to be with him.

227
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,240
I can feel his soul.

228
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:36,150
I talk to him every day.

229
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,790
Even though he never responds,

230
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,040
in the ringing

231
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,270
of the New Year's bell,

232
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,510
maybe I can hold his hand.

233
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,550
You bought this magic formation online,
didn't you?

234
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:57,550
Is it reliable?

235
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,440
Wild guess again.

236
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,240
I'm not

237
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,150
that stupid.

238
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,600
You even broke up with your boyfriend

239
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,240
for him.

240
00:10:04,550 --> 00:10:05,610
That's different.

241
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,550
Even without GB38,

242
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,360
he and I would still

243
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,220
have broken up.

244
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,370
I never liked Li Lei at all.

245
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,320
Then why

246
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,520
did you get together?

247
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,130
He chased me for 7 or 8 years.

248
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:17,600
I just went soft on him for a moment.

249
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,530
There are 3 minutes left

250
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,260
until the new year.

251
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,960
Han Meimei and I

252
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,300
met in junior high school.

253
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,390
To win her over,

254
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,290
I memorized a lot of English words.

255
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,630
We went to the same high school

256
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,260
and then the same university.

257
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,190
I chased her all the time.

258
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,750
I'm so tired.

259
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,910
But in the end,

260
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,630
she still didn't fall for me.

261
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:00,750
You are a very

262
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,870
loving boy.

263
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,400
You are still young.

264
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,120
There's a long road ahead.

265
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,030
You will definitely meet a girl

266
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,030
whom you love very much

267
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,390
and who loves you back.

268
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,770
My love has been exhausted.

269
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,120
I will never love again.

270
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,520
Stop being so depressed.

271
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:17,870
I don't get it either.

272
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,960
How could a person

273
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,790
like a skull?

274
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,870
Actually,

275
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,310
she just doesn't like me.

276
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:31,870
You see,

277
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,220
in many things,

278
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,500
effort is useless.

279
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,170
You've figured it out?

280
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,590
You're right.

281
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,290
Maybe when I wake up tomorrow,

282
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,050
my happiness will come.

283
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,630
I will meet

284
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,510
a new girl.

285
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,030
I will like her very much.

286
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,120
And she will like me too.

287
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:08,010
It's midnight.

288
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,320
It's a new year.

289
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,580
I should go now.

290
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,670
When you get a new girlfriend,

291
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,630
bring her to the store.

292
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,030
I'll treat you to coffee.

293
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,530
Happy New Year.

294
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:56,440
GB38,

295
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,140
